      <ing>
        <amt>
          <qty>1</qty>
          <unit>teaspoon</unit></amt>
        <item>Baking soda</item></ing>
      <ing>
        <amt>
          <qty>1/2</qty>
          <unit>teaspoons</unit></amt>
        <item>Salt</item></ing></ingredients>
    <directions>
      <step>  Heat oven to 350ยบF. Grease(not oil) bottom only of 9x5 or 8x4-inch loaf
  pan. In large bowl, blend first 6 ingredients beat 1 minute at medium
  speed. Stir in remaining ingredients just until dry ingredients are
  moistened. Pour batter into prepared pan. Bake at 350ยบ for 50 to 60 minutes
  or until toothpick inserted into center comes out clean. Cool 5 minutes;
  remove from pan. Cool completely.
  
  Makes 1 loaf
  
